app/
  bin/                  #Files for command-line execution
  lib/
    appname.rb
    appname/            #Classes and so on
  Rakefile              #Running tests
  README
  test,spec,features/   #Whichever means of testing you go for
  appname.gemspec       #If it's a gem
  
  For Documentation -> http://tomdoc.org/
  
  http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4687659/should-one-use-dashes-or-underscores-when-naming-a-gem-with-more-than-one-word